body:
Hi everyone. 
The discussion this week on Ask Riot is about the new Honor system. I was thinking...what if we perform really well individually in a game but end up losing the match and **do not get honored for our effort**. Do you think we should at least gain a little progress on our honor system? Well i think so. Apparently the reason why there is no progress bar for the honor system is because it spans over the duration of a whole season, thus making it hard to see a ever so **slooooooooow grind towards higher honor levels**. Anyways let me know what ya&#039;ll think.
